    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>垃圾装载王 (Garbage Packer)</strong><br>进入《垃圾装载王》的驾驶座，这是一款充满挑战的物理模拟垃圾车游戏！掌控前装式垃圾车，掌握垃圾收集和压缩的艺术。通过逼真的控制和引人入胜的玩法，感受管理垃圾车载量的刺激与策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>物理模拟控制：</strong> 操作垃圾车的机械臂，拾起垃圾箱，将垃圾倒入车内，并用压缩机最大限度地节省空间。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219550/extras/b3a415101336c50af9184ae69e6a5f75.poster.avif?t=1746942756\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219550/extras/b3a415101336c50af9184ae69e6a5f75.webm?t=1746942756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219550/extras/b3a415101336c50af9184ae69e6a5f75.mp4?t=1746942756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>策略性装载：</strong> 精心管理垃圾车有限的容量，通过合理压缩和安排垃圾来最大化装载量。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219550/extras/7be488c5f2937f1894f443d1bcad2815.poster.avif?t=1746942756\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219550/extras/7be488c5f2937f1894f443d1bcad2815.webm?t=1746942756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219550/extras/7be488c5f2937f1894f443d1bcad2815.mp4?t=1746942756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>评分系统：</strong> 将垃圾卸载到垃圾场，根据收集和压缩的垃圾量获得评分。你能否超越竞争对手，成为装载高手？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沉浸式视角：</strong> 在第一人称和第三人称视角之间切换，从不同角度体验游戏的精彩。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>排行榜：</strong> 与全球玩家竞争，看谁能装载最多垃圾，登上排行榜的巅峰！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是否有能力成为终极垃圾装载冠军？抓住控制器，开始装载，展示你的技能吧！</p>",
